The final Democratic presidential debate of 2020 was a dispiriting affair for reasons that went far beyond the politics of it.
Georgia has postponed its primary, which was slated for next Tuesday, and Louisiana’s April 4 primary has likewise been delayed.
Joe Biden is fortunate that Bernie Sanders was feeling conciliatory under the circumstances, because Biden lied, lied and lied throughout the evening.
The CNN moderators didn’t bother trying to call Biden on his loose relationship with the truth, but Sanders persistently did so.
Bernie Sanders told us as much last night, just as he has for the full term of his public life.